lead_paragraph: Danuel House had 16 points, including two free throws with 2.1 seconds remaining, to lift No. 21 Texas A&M to a 68-66 victory over Mississippi State on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: House Leads No. 21 Texas A&M Over Mississippi State 68-66
